    A generic interface for DAO objects handling JoinHolder interfaces.

    Helper interface for use with the Spring IOC container and DAO beans that handle JoinHolder entities.

    A generic DAO interface containing additional methods for accessing JoinHolders and the persisted entities they join in a paginated way.
